<span class='tline' id='l147' data-llen='5542:5583'><span class='krp-note'>為誅責有官/君子之刑</span>儆于有位<span class='krp-note'>以儆戒于/有位之人</span>曰<span class='krp-note'>其刑/曰</span>敢有恒舞于</span><br/>
